課程概述 Course Description
       熱力學與統計力學導論是物理學的一個重要分支，主要研究物體的熱現象。 本課程將包含統計力學導論，是熱現象的微觀理論。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To present the basic knowledge of statistical mechanics。To introduce the basic computational techniques of statistical mechanics。To introduce  the concepts of phase transitions。 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Review of Thermodynamics and the conditions for thermodynamical equilibrium。2Definition of microstates, microcanonical ensemble, and the first law of thermodynamics。3Canonical ensemble and the derivation of the partition function。4The connection between the canonical ensemble and the first law of thermodynamics。5First test (March 26)。Applications of canonical partition6The theorem of equipartition of energy and the virial theorem and their applications 。7Grand canonical ensemble and the derivation of the grand canonical partition function。8Information theory:  the entropy function and Fisher information, their applications to statistical mechanics。Second test。9More on the applications of information theory to statistical mechanics。10Second test (April 30)。Application of the grand canonical ensemble to the blackbody radiation。11More applications of the grand canonical ensemble。12Bose-Einstein statistics and Fermi-Dirac statistics。13The theory of Bose-Einstein condensation。14Third test (May 28)。White dwarf and neutron stars。15Thermodynamic equilibrium and phase transitions 。16More on thermodynamic equilibrium。17Review。18Final exam (June 30)。 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


